00:31:33,882 --> 00:31:35,315
l wouldn't put that on.

667
00:31:35,402 --> 00:31:38,314
lt's a bit...not the right mood.

668
00:31:38,402 --> 00:31:39,357
Oh?

669
00:31:41,082 --> 00:31:42,993
And what's the right mood?

670
00:31:44,362 --> 00:31:46,273
