671
00:31:46,362 --> 00:31:47,795
something...you know.

672
00:31:47,882 --> 00:31:48,837
What?

673
00:31:50,282 --> 00:31:51,715
You know, just...

674
00:31:51,802 --> 00:31:54,521
something not as...
sweary and loud.

675
00:31:56,562 --> 00:31:58,951
Paul, that's the most
romantic thing

676
00:31:59,042 --> 00:32:00,953
