726
00:33:52,722 --> 00:33:54,155
and you're dead wrong.

727
00:33:54,242 --> 00:33:57,154
l'm capable of commitment
and all that stuff.

728
00:33:57,242 --> 00:33:58,960
lf it doesn't happen with you,

729
