00:34:49,162 --> 00:34:50,595
Well, l don't know.

750
00:34:50,682 --> 00:34:52,593
lt sinks in after a while.

751
00:34:52,682 --> 00:34:54,115
What else has sunk in?

752
00:34:54,202 --> 00:34:57,319
