goal-hanger is?

754
00:34:59,402 --> 00:35:01,358
l'm not turning into a moron.

755
00:35:01,442 --> 00:35:04,115
OK, l know they're
top of the League.

756
00:35:04,202 --> 00:35:05,635
That's easy to remember.

757
00:35:05,722 --> 00:35:08,156
And l know that
Alan ''Smudger'' Smith

758
00:35:08,242 --> 00:35:10,153
has scored most of the goals.

759
00:35:10,242 --> 00:35:11,675
But it doesn't...

