00:35:15,282 --> 00:35:16,681
To a football match?

764
00:35:16,762 --> 00:35:18,673
Yeah. l thought l should.

765
00:35:18,762 --> 00:35:20,480
Ooh. l tell you, girl,

766
00:35:20,562 --> 00:35:22,280
you'd better watch yourself.

