775
00:35:36,522 --> 00:35:37,557
Rubbish!

776
00:35:37,642 --> 00:35:39,075
lt's true!

777
00:35:39,162 --> 00:35:40,595
You get colonised.

778
00:35:40,682 --> 00:35:43,116
Your native culture
gets driven out

779
00:35:43,202 --> 00:35:45,113
and it's replaced by stuff

780
00:35:45,202 --> 00:35:47,318
you don't even wanna know about.

781
00:35:47,402 --> 00:35:49,313
They're like
bloody missionaries.

782
00:35:49,402 --> 00:35:52,314
