802
00:36:35,962 --> 00:36:37,395
Well, near, yeah.

803
00:36:37,482 --> 00:36:39,393
[Man] How near is near?

804
00:36:39,482 --> 00:36:40,995
Place called Maidenhead.

805
00:36:41,082 --> 00:36:41,992
Maidenhead?

806
00:36:42,082 --> 00:36:43,481
Maidenhead in Berkshire?

807
00:36:43,562 --> 00:36:45,314
Two miles down the road?

808
00:36:45,402 --> 00:36:46,835
More like six.

809
00:36:46,922 --> 00:36:48,799
Bit nearer Reading than Arsenal.

810
00:36:48,882 --> 00:36:51,794
