to get to Birmingham?

830
00:37:36,682 --> 00:37:38,593
Couple of hours. Maybe three.

831
00:37:38,682 --> 00:37:40,400
But we'll be there by two?

832
00:37:40,482 --> 00:37:41,437
Oh, sure.

833
