00:37:48,082 --> 00:37:49,481
How d'you mean?

835
00:37:49,562 --> 00:37:50,995
l thought you might like

836
00:37:51,082 --> 00:37:53,676
to meet Jane and
the kids for lunch.

837
00:37:53,762 --> 00:37:55,673
Then maybe take 'em to the zoo

838
00:37:55,762 --> 00:37:57,195
or pictures...somewhere.

839
00:37:58,962 --> 00:38:00,680
They've been over this week

840
00:38:00,762 --> 00:38:02,161
visiting their grandmother.

841
00:38:02,242 --> 00:38:03,675
They'd love to meet you.

842
00:38:03,762 --> 00:38:06,356
You don't mean instead
of the game, do you?

843
00:38:06,442 --> 00:38:07,841
We couldn't do both.

844
00:38:07,922 --> 00:38:10,834
You didn't get
any tickets, did you?

845
00:38:10,922 --> 00:38:13,356
The tickets are
waiting for us there.

846
00:38:13,442 --> 00:38:16,354
So you're telling me
you've got tickets

847
00:38:16,442 --> 00:38:19,752
but you wanna go and see
''The Jungle Book''?

848
00:38:21,562 --> 00:38:23,280
You're teasing me, aren't you?

849
00:38:23,362 --> 00:38:25,273
We don't have to go to Arsenal

850
00:38:25,362 --> 00:38:27,273
every time l'm in London, do we?

851
00:38:27,362 --> 00:38:30,115
l thought we were
beyond that stage.

852
00:38:31,802 --> 00:38:34,236
We'll never be
beyond that stage.

