00:51:41,362 --> 00:51:44,274
l changed my mind about
that Head of Year job,

1099
00:51:44,362 --> 00:51:45,795
if it's not too late.

1100
00:51:45,882 --> 00:51:48,316
No. No, excellent.
l'm very pleased.

1101
00:51:48,402 --> 00:51:50,313
l've had a couple
of applications

