of beating a team

1144
00:53:20,562 --> 00:53:21,995
1 5 or 20-nil?

1145
00:53:22,082 --> 00:53:23,481
lt's brilliant fun!

1146
00:53:23,562 --> 00:53:26,474
All right.
Just take it easy, eh?

1147
00:53:26,562 --> 00:53:27,995
You're like vultures.

1148
00:53:28,082 --> 00:53:29,515
Now go on!

1149
00:53:29,602 --> 00:53:31,035
Come on, lads!

1150
00:53:47,202 --> 00:53:48,112
