00:56:53,922 --> 00:56:55,833
'Arsenal five, Norwich City nil.

1223
00:56:55,922 --> 00:56:57,833
'Alan Smith the man of the match

1224
00:56:57,922 --> 00:56:59,355
'with two goals,

1225
00:56:59,442 --> 00:57:01,353
'one of them
a splendid effort...'

1226
00:57:01,442 --> 00:57:02,841
Everything's happening at once

1227
00:57:02,922 --> 00:57:04,321
and it's brilliant.

1228
00:57:04,402 --> 00:57:07,314
Stick with me.
No way we won't win the League.

1229
00:57:07,402 --> 00:57:08,835
lt's all you, is it?

1230
00:57:08,922 --> 00:57:11,834
Nothing to do
with George, Smithy, Rocky

1231
00:57:11,922 --> 00:57:13,355
or me buying sugar mice?

1232
00:57:13,442 --> 00:57:15,876
