00:57:15,962 --> 00:57:17,554
l felt brilliant the day

1234
00:57:17,642 --> 00:57:20,554
we got knocked out
of the League by Walsall.

1235
00:57:20,642 --> 00:57:22,075
Got a pay rise,

1236
00:57:22,162 --> 00:57:25,074
got off with Caroline Walsh
the night before.

1237
00:57:25,162 --> 00:57:27,596
Fat lot of fucking notice
this lot took.

1238
00:57:27,682 --> 00:57:30,594
Some of us have it,
some of us haven't.

1239
00:57:30,682 --> 00:57:33,594
You must've had
a shitty life for 1 8 years.

1240
00:57:33,682 --> 00:57:35,593
l haven't had it all the time

1241
00:57:35,682 --> 00:57:38,242
but l've got it
this season in spades.

1242
00:57:43,762 --> 00:57:45,161
Did you go?

1243
00:57:45,242 --> 00:57:47,153
Yeah. We were great, weren't we?

1244
00:57:47,242 --> 00:57:49,153
My mum wants a season ticket.

1245
00:57:49,242 --> 00:57:50,960
Can l have a quick word?

1246
00:57:51,042 --> 00:57:53,954
We're just talking
about the rout of Norwich.

1247
00:57:54,042 --> 00:57:55,555
Yes, saw it on TV.

1248
00:57:55,642 --> 00:57:56,961
Very impressive.

1249
00:57:57,042 --> 00:57:59,431
lt's good
that Alan Smith's back.

1250
00:57:59,522 --> 00:58:00,921
Yeah. Run along, Robert.

1251
00:58:01,002 --> 00:58:02,913
l had a word with the Governors.

1252
00:58:03,002 --> 00:58:04,913
They'll be happy
to interview you

1253
00:58:05,002 --> 00:58:06,276
for Head of Year.

1254
00:58:06,362 --> 00:58:07,590
Thanks, Ted.

1255
00:58:07,682 --> 00:58:11,118
Ted...l'm not planning
to make a habit of this

1256
00:58:11,202 --> 00:58:13,636
if that's what
you're worried about.

1257
00:58:13,722 --> 00:58:16,236
lt's something out
of the ordinary for me.

1258
00:58:16,322 --> 00:58:18,233
Just be prepared, OK?

1259
00:58:18,322 --> 00:58:21,234
School Governors
can be a funny lot.

1260
00:58:24,162 --> 00:58:26,073
[Radio]
'..Still Middlesborough nil,

1261
00:58:26,162 --> 00:58:27,561
'Arsenal nil...'

1262
00:58:35,762 --> 00:58:37,161
You're kidding. No way.

1263
00:58:39,322 --> 00:58:40,721
