1270
00:58:54,962 --> 00:58:56,361
Do they leave much mess?

1271
00:58:56,442 --> 00:58:59,354
No. Shall l leave you
to look around?

1272
00:58:59,442 --> 00:59:00,557
Thanks, yeah.

1273
00:59:02,762 --> 00:59:06,675
What does it matter
how close to the ground you live

1274
00:59:06,762 --> 00:59:09,481
as long as you can
come to the games?

1275
00:59:09,562 --> 00:59:11,996
When l was a kid,
l read this...

1276
00:59:12,082 --> 00:59:14,994
story about what used
to happen round here

1277
00:59:15,082 --> 00:59:17,915
on Cup Final days
if Arsenal were playing.

1278
00:59:18,002 --> 00:59:19,640
They'd have this procession.

1279
00:59:19,722 --> 00:59:22,634
The women and kids
dressed up in fancy dress

1280
00:59:22,722 --> 00:59:25,634
and led the men going
to Wembley to the station.

1281
00:59:31,122 --> 00:59:32,555
l lived in Maidenhead.

1282
00:59:32,642 --> 00:59:35,156
- What did we have there?
- Money, decent schools,

1283
00:59:35,242 --> 00:59:36,960
holidays abroad, enough food.

1284
00:59:37,042 --> 00:59:38,953
Yeah. You're right, yeah.

1285
00:59:39,042 --> 00:59:40,270
l was lucky.

1286
00:59:40,362 --> 00:59:41,795
But l was rootless, too.

1287
00:59:41,882 --> 00:59:43,793
l didn't have
anything like that.

1288
00:59:43,882 --> 00:59:45,793
Nothing l could be proud of,

1289
00:59:45,882 --> 00:59:49,318
nothing l can look back on
and feel sentimental about

1290
00:59:49,402 --> 00:59:51,836
except telly programmes
and pop music.

1291
00:59:51,922 --> 00:59:53,321
But it's different here.

1292
00:59:56,562 --> 00:59:59,281
Anyway...it's close to the tube.

1293
00:59:59,362 --> 01:00:01,796
lt's 50 minutes
from the West End.

1294
01:00:01,882 --> 01:00:03,600
lt's not far from school.

1295
01:00:03,682 --> 01:00:05,115
l'm not prepared

1296
01:00:05,202 --> 01:00:06,635
to indulge your fantasies.

1297
01:00:06,722 --> 01:00:08,155
The best thing for you

1298
01:00:08,242 --> 01:00:09,960
would be to get further away,

1299
01:00:10,042 --> 01:00:11,475
not a few yards nearer.

1300
01:00:11,562 --> 01:00:13,678
- lt doesn't feel like that.
- Tough.

1301
01:00:15,162 --> 01:00:16,561
