1306
01:00:31,362 --> 01:00:33,273
Tell me again what was wrong

1307
01:00:33,362 --> 01:00:35,751
with that place in...
Creighton Avenue.

1308
01:00:35,842 --> 01:00:37,560
The one with the garden.

1309
01:00:37,642 --> 01:00:40,031
'Despite all their control,
Arsenal...'

1310
01:00:40,122 --> 01:00:41,521
l'm talking to myself.

1311
01:00:41,602 --> 01:00:43,991
Somewhere a bit
further north, anyway.

1312
01:00:44,082 --> 01:00:44,992
Bounds Green?

1313
01:00:45,082 --> 01:00:46,481
'John Lukic prepares

1314
01:00:46,562 --> 01:00:48,280
to play it downfield...'

1315
01:00:48,362 --> 01:00:49,715
Watford?

1316
01:00:49,802 --> 01:00:51,713
'..lnto the
Middlesborough half...'

1317
01:00:51,802 --> 01:00:54,236
How about Darlington?
There's a team there.

1318
01:00:54,322 --> 01:00:55,232
'Goal!'

1319
01:00:55,322 --> 01:00:56,755
YES! Yes! Yes! Yes!

1320
01:00:56,842 --> 01:00:58,400
Helsinki. Helsinki United

1321
01:00:58,482 --> 01:01:00,393
are really good this season.

1322
01:01:00,482 --> 01:01:02,916
[Paul sings] One Martin Hayes!

1323
01:01:03,002 --> 01:01:05,436
There's only one Martin Hayes!

1324
01:01:05,522 --> 01:01:07,035
One Martin...

1325
01:01:08,842 --> 01:01:10,560
[Man] So, Paul...

1326
01:01:10,642 --> 01:01:11,597
Confident?

1327
01:01:12,842 --> 01:01:14,753
Sorry, not about the job.

1328
01:01:14,842 --> 01:01:17,754
About what's going on
down the road.

1329
01:01:19,042 --> 01:01:21,761
Arsenal. My boy tells me
you're a fan.

1330
01:01:21,842 --> 01:01:23,161
Oh, right.

1331
01:01:23,242 --> 01:01:26,040
Well, er...so far, so good.

1332
01:01:26,122 --> 01:01:27,555
Season ticket holder?

1333
01:01:27,642 --> 01:01:28,552
Yes.

1334
01:01:28,642 --> 01:01:29,552
Whereabouts?

1335
01:01:29,642 --> 01:01:31,041
Er, North Bank.

1336
01:01:31,122 --> 01:01:33,033
Right, shall we, um...?

1337
01:01:33,122 --> 01:01:35,033
Who d'you think we should sign?

1338
01:01:35,122 --> 01:01:36,840
Think we need a new striker?

1339
01:01:36,922 --> 01:01:38,037
Er...

1340
01:01:38,122 --> 01:01:41,034
l'm delighted
we didn't get Kerry Dixon.

1341
01:01:41,122 --> 01:01:43,556
Ray... Ray, l think
we should, um...

1342
01:01:43,642 --> 01:01:45,075
